<paragraph blockId="5.[264,1323,1137,1883]" lastBlockId="6.[264,1324,284,1150]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
The nomenclatural situation in this group is rather complicated and needs the following comments: In 
<number box="[505,566,1297,1323]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1989.0">1989</number>
, Holyñski published “The content and systematic position of 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1851" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1851" box="[264,594,1337,1363]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[264,437,1337,1362]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[445,594,1337,1363]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1851) Orden III. Coleopteros, 1 - 285. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 5, 1 - 563." type="journal article" year="1851">
Solier, 
<number box="[530,594,1337,1363]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1851.0">1851</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
”. The introductory paragraph of this paper is the most crucial for the whole case: he misquoted the date of Solier´s monograph — 
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[1078,1222,1377,1403]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1849) Orden III. Coleopteros, 105 - 380, 414 - 511. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 4, 81 - 511." type="journal article" year="1849">
Solier, 
<number box="[1163,1222,1377,1403]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1849.0">1849</number>
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1282,1323,1377,1403]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">not</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[264,323,1417,1443]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1851) Orden III. Coleopteros, 1 - 285. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 5, 1 - 563." type="journal article" year="1851">
<number box="[264,323,1417,1443]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1851.0">1851</number>
</bibRefCitation>
(evidently having followed 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos" box="[655,804,1417,1443]" pageId="5" pageNumber="10" refString="Cobos, A. (1956) Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria), 5, 103 - 165." type="journal article" year="1956">
Cobos, 
<number box="[745,804,1417,1443]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1956.0">1956</number>
</bibRefCitation>
who also synonymized in the same revision the genera 
<taxonomicName box="[399,521,1457,1482]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[399,521,1457,1482]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Brasilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Germain, 1856" authorityName="Germain" authorityYear="1856" box="[585,911,1457,1483]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Ctenoderus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[585,720,1457,1482]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Ctenoderus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Germain" box="[731,911,1457,1483]" pageId="5" pageNumber="10" refString="Germain, P. (1856) Descripcion de coleopteros de diversas especies que non se hallan en la obra del senor Gay. Anales de la Universidad. Republica de Chile, 1855, 386 - 407." type="journal article" year="1856">
Germain, 
<number box="[852,911,1457,1483]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1856.0">1856</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
with the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1849" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1849" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1149,1322,1457,1482]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[264,408,1497,1523]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1849) Orden III. Coleopteros, 105 - 380, 414 - 511. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 4, 81 - 511." type="journal article" year="1849">
Solier, 
<number box="[349,408,1497,1523]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1849.0">1849</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
of his widely accepted genus 
<taxonomicName box="[773,879,1497,1522]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[773,879,1497,1522]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); this problem was clearly explained by Bellamy (
<number box="[421,484,1537,1563]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1999.0">1999</number>
), i.e. there is no mention of 
<taxonomicName box="[831,971,1537,1563]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Buprestidae</taxonomicName>
in the volume dated 
<number box="[1230,1289,1537,1563]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1851.0">1851</number>
of Solier’s work. In the same paragraph Holyñski mentioned ” 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1851" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="marginicollis">
<emphasis box="[984,1322,1577,1602]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora marginicollis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[264,409,1617,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1851) Orden III. Coleopteros, 1 - 285. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 5, 1 - 563." type="journal article" year="1851">
Solier, 
<number box="[350,409,1617,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1851.0">1851</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName authority="Erichson, 1834" authorityName="Erichson" authorityYear="1834" box="[454,800,1617,1643]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="verecunda">
<emphasis box="[454,610,1617,1642]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">A. verecunda</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Erichson" box="[620,800,1617,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="10" refString="Erichson, W. F. (1834) Meyen's Beitrage zur Zoologie, gesammelt auf einer Reise um die Erde, und. W. Erichsons und H. Burmeisters Beschreibung and Abbildungen der auf dieser Reise gesammelten Insecten. Nova Acta Physico-Medica Academiae Caesareae-Leopoldino-Carolinae, Naturae Curiosorum 16, Suppl. 1, 219 - 184, 41 col. pl." type="journal article" year="1834">
Erichson, 
<number box="[740,800,1617,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1834.0">1834</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
) as the 
<typeStatus box="[897,947,1617,1643]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1851" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[349,503,1657,1683]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1851) Orden III. Coleopteros, 1 - 285. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 5, 1 - 563." type="journal article" year="1851">
Solier, 
<number box="[439,503,1657,1683]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1851.0">1851</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.” 
<collectingCountry box="[533,565,1657,1683]" name="American Samoa" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">As</collectingCountry>
already explained by Bellamy (
<number box="[976,1039,1657,1683]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1999.0">1999</number>
), 
<taxonomicName box="[1067,1262,1657,1682]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="marginicollis">
<emphasis box="[1067,1262,1657,1682]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">A. marginicollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described quite independently (before the description of 
<taxonomicName box="[930,1103,1697,1722]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[930,1103,1697,1722]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and cannot be, in this way, the 
<typeStatus box="[426,476,1737,1763]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<emphasis box="[615,796,1737,1762]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<taxonomicName box="[615,792,1737,1762]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">Cylindrophora</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName box="[939,1112,1737,1762]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[939,1112,1737,1762]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described in the following text with two species included: 
<taxonomicName authority="Guerin-Meneville, 1830" authorityName="Guerin-Meneville" authorityYear="1830" box="[795,1260,1777,1803]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Buprestis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bella">
<emphasis box="[795,970,1777,1802]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Buprestis bella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Guerin-Meneville" box="[976,1260,1777,1803]" pageId="5" pageNumber="10" refString="Guerin-Meneville, F. E. (1830) Crustacees, Arachnides et Insectes, 1 - 319. In: Duperrey, L. J.: Vo yage autour du monde, erecute par Ordre du Roi, sur la corvette de La Majeste, la Coquille, pendant les annees 1822, 1823, 1824, et 1825, sous le ministere et conformement aux instructions de S. E. M. le Marquis de Clermont - Tonnerre, ministre de la marine. Zoologie, Tom. II, Part. II, 1 re Div., 319 pp, 22 col. pl." type="book" year="1830">
Guérin­Menéville, 
<number box="[1201,1260,1777,1803]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1830.0">1830</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Molina, 1782" authorityName="Molina" authorityYear="1782" box="[463,886,1817,1843]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chrysomela" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maulica">
<emphasis box="[463,711,1817,1842]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Chrysomela maulica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Molina" box="[722,886,1817,1843]" pageId="5" pageNumber="11" refString="Molina, J. I. (1782) Saggio sulla storia naturale del Chili. Bologna, 367 pp." type="book" year="1782">
Molina, 
<number box="[826,886,1817,1843]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1782.0">1782</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
) and ” 
<taxonomicName authority="Germar" authorityName="Germar" box="[972,1308,1817,1843]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Buprestis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="concinna">
<emphasis box="[972,1202,1817,1842]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Buprestis concinna</emphasis>
Germar
</taxonomicName>
”. The combination ” 
<taxonomicName authority="Germar" authorityName="Germar" box="[488,732,1857,1883]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Buprestis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="concinna">
<emphasis box="[488,630,1857,1882]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">B. concinna</emphasis>
Germar
</taxonomicName>
” doesn´t exist (
<taxonomicName box="[920,1147,1857,1882]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Buprestis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="concinna">
<emphasis box="[920,1147,1857,1882]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Buprestis concinna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Mannerheim" box="[305,530,284,310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="11" refString="Mannerheim, C. G. von, (1837) Enumeration des Buprestides, et description de quelques nouvelles especes de cette tribu de la famille des Sternoxes, de la collection de M. Le Comte Mannerheim. Bulletin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscou, 8, 1 - 126." type="journal article" year="1837">
Mannerheim 
<number box="[467,530,284,310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1837.0">1837</number>
</bibRefCitation>
); in this case 
<taxonomicName authority="Molina, 1782" authorityName="Molina" authorityYear="1782" box="[707,1130,284,310]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chrysomela" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maulica">
<emphasis box="[707,956,284,309]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Chrysomela maulica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Molina" box="[967,1130,284,310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="11" refString="Molina, J. I. (1782) Saggio sulla storia naturale del Chili. Bologna, 367 pp." type="book" year="1782">
Molina, 
<number box="[1071,1130,284,310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1782.0">1782</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(with synonym 
<taxonomicName authority="Guerin-Meneville, 1830" authorityName="Guerin-Meneville" authorityYear="1830" box="[264,737,324,350]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Buprestis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bella">
<emphasis box="[264,441,324,349]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Buprestis bella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Guerin-Meneville" box="[450,737,324,350]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Guerin-Meneville, F. E. (1830) Crustacees, Arachnides et Insectes, 1 - 319. In: Duperrey, L. J.: Vo yage autour du monde, erecute par Ordre du Roi, sur la corvette de La Majeste, la Coquille, pendant les annees 1822, 1823, 1824, et 1825, sous le ministere et conformement aux instructions de S. E. M. le Marquis de Clermont - Tonnerre, ministre de la marine. Zoologie, Tom. II, Part. II, 1 re Div., 319 pp, 22 col. pl." type="book" year="1830">
Guérin­Menéville, 
<number box="[677,737,324,350]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1830.0">1830</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
) must be the 
<typeStatus box="[901,952,324,350]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1849" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1849" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[341,483,364,390]" pageId="6" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1849) Orden III. Coleopteros, 105 - 380, 414 - 511. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 4, 81 - 511." type="journal article" year="1849">
Solier, 
<number box="[425,483,364,390]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1849.0">1849</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
— a fact which changes the whole situation in Anthaxiina and Curina.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1150]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Because 
<bibRefCitation author="Holynski" box="[421,617,403,430]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Holynski, R. (1989) The content and systematic position of Cylindrophora Solier, 1851 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Elytron (Barcelona), 3, 163 - 167." type="journal article" year="1989">
Holyñski (
<number box="[548,609,404,430]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1989.0">1989</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
supposed (and I do agree with him) ” 
<taxonomicName box="[1091,1249,404,429]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="verecunda">
<emphasis box="[1091,1249,404,429]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. verecunda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="marginicollis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. marginicollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
)” not to be congeneric with 
<taxonomicName box="[760,866,444,469]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[760,866,444,469]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
or with the rest of species included so far in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Cobos (1956)" authorityName="Cobos" authorityYear="1956" box="[491,905,484,510]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[491,664,484,509]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
sensu 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos" box="[742,905,484,510]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Cobos, A. (1956) Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria), 5, 103 - 165." type="journal article" year="1956">
Cobos (
<number box="[833,896,484,510]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1956.0">1956</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and because he supposed it erroneously to be the 
<typeStatus box="[446,496,524,550]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<emphasis box="[630,809,524,549]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<taxonomicName box="[630,806,524,549]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">Cylindrophora</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
he created for the remaining species a new subgeneric name: 
<taxonomicName authority="Holynski, 1989" authorityName="Holynski" authorityYear="1989" box="[484,774,563,590]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Bilyaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[484,582,564,589]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Bilyaxia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Holynski" box="[589,774,563,590]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Holynski, R. (1989) The content and systematic position of Cylindrophora Solier, 1851 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Elytron (Barcelona), 3, 163 - 167." type="journal article" year="1989">
Holyñski, 
<number box="[712,774,564,590]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1989.0">1989</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. He also recognized that two more species formerly included in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Cobos (1956)" authorityName="Cobos" authorityYear="1956" box="[665,1095,604,630]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[665,838,604,629]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
sensu 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos" box="[929,1095,604,630]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Cobos, A. (1956) Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria), 5, 103 - 165." type="journal article" year="1956">
Cobos (
<number box="[1026,1087,604,630]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1956.0">1956</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
should have been shifted to a separate genus: 
<taxonomicName box="[610,734,644,669]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="oyarcei">
<emphasis box="[610,734,644,669]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. oyarcei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(described in the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Gory &amp; Laporte, 1838" authorityName="Gory &amp; Laporte" authorityYear="1838" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1041,1106,644,669]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Curis</emphasis>
Gory &amp; Laporte, 
<number box="[264,324,684,710]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1838.0">1838</number>
</taxonomicName>
) and 
<taxonomicName authority="Germain, 1856" authorityName="Germain" authorityYear="1856" box="[396,702,684,710]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloris">
<emphasis box="[396,513,684,709]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. chloris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Germain" box="[523,702,684,710]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Germain, P. (1856) Descripcion de coleopteros de diversas especies que non se hallan en la obra del senor Gay. Anales de la Universidad. Republica de Chile, 1855, 386 - 407." type="journal article" year="1856">
Germain, 
<number box="[643,702,684,710]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1856.0">1856</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(described as the only species of the genus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Ctenoderus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Ctenoderus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and he suggested to treat them in a separate subgenus 
<taxonomicName box="[1025,1160,724,749]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Ctenoderus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1025,1160,724,749]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Ctenoderus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[264,329,764,789]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[264,329,764,789]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Curis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(now 
<taxonomicName authority="Dejean, 1836" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1836" box="[408,660,764,790]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Selagis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[408,493,764,789]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Selagis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dejean" box="[502,660,764,790]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A., (Juli) (1836) Catalogue des Coleopteres de la collection de M. le comte Dejean. Troisieme edition, revue, corrigee et augmentee, livraisons 1 - 4, Mequignon-Marvis, Paris, 384 pp. [Selagis, p. 89]" type="book chapter" year="1836">
Dejean, 
<number box="[601,660,764,790]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1836.0">1836</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
— see 
<bibRefCitation author="Bellamy" box="[754,932,764,790]" pageId="6" pageNumber="9" refString="Bellamy, C. L. (2003) An illustrated summary of the higher classification of the superfamily Buprestoidea (Coleoptera). Folia Heyrovskyana, Suppl. 10, 1 - 197." type="book chapter" year="2003">
Bellamy, 
<number box="[868,932,764,790]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="2003.0">2003</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). The position of the next ”enigmatic” species mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="Holynski" box="[607,800,803,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Holynski, R. (1989) The content and systematic position of Cylindrophora Solier, 1851 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Elytron (Barcelona), 3, 163 - 167." type="journal article" year="1989">
Holyñski (
<number box="[731,792,804,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1989.0">1989</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
— 
<taxonomicName authority="Kerremans, 1913" authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1913" box="[841,1264,804,830]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cinctipennis">
<emphasis box="[841,1055,804,829]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Curis cinctipennis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Kerremans" box="[1061,1264,804,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="11" refString="Kerremans, C. (1913) Collections recueillies par M. E. - R. Wagner dans la Republique Argentine. Coleopteres buprestides. Bulletin du Museum d'Histoire Naturelle, 19, 580 - 589." type="journal article" year="1913">
Kerremans, 
<number box="[1205,1264,804,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1913.0">1913</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was solved by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos" box="[387,549,844,870]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Cobos, A. (1971) Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria), 16, 5 - 235." type="journal article" year="1971">
Cobos (
<number box="[479,540,844,870]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1971.0">1971</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
who attributed it to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName box="[954,1127,844,869]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[954,1127,844,869]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Having studied the 
<typeStatus box="[307,413,884,910]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">holotype</typeStatus>
, I agree and find this species to be very near to 
<taxonomicName authority="Cobos, 1956" authorityName="Cobos" authorityYear="1956" box="[970,1318,884,910]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Bilyaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bucki">
<emphasis box="[970,1138,884,909]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Bilyaxia bucki</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos" box="[1155,1308,884,910]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Cobos, A. (1956) Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria), 5, 103 - 165." type="journal article" year="1956">
Cobos, 
<number box="[1245,1308,884,910]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1956.0">1956</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1150]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
I consider the differences between 
<taxonomicName box="[721,806,924,949]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Selagis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[721,806,924,949]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Selagis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[821,956,924,949]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Ctenoderus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[821,956,924,949]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Ctenoderus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1013,1186,924,949]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1013,1186,924,949]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be sufficient for their treatment as separate genera of Curina 
<bibRefCitation author="Holynski" box="[922,1110,963,990]" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Holynski, R. (1988) Remarks on the general classification of Buprestidae Leach as applied to Maoraxiina Hol. Folia Entomologica Hungarica, 49, 49 - 54." type="journal article" year="1988">
Holyñski, 
<number box="[1048,1110,964,990]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1988.0">1988</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; moreover a new genus name must be created for the remaining species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Erichson, 1834" authorityName="Erichson" authorityYear="1834" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="verecunda">
<emphasis box="[951,1190,1004,1029]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Anthaxia verecunda</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Erichson" pageId="6" pageNumber="10" refString="Erichson, W. F. (1834) Meyen's Beitrage zur Zoologie, gesammelt auf einer Reise um die Erde, und. W. Erichsons und H. Burmeisters Beschreibung and Abbildungen der auf dieser Reise gesammelten Insecten. Nova Acta Physico-Medica Academiae Caesareae-Leopoldino-Carolinae, Naturae Curiosorum 16, Suppl. 1, 219 - 184, 41 col. pl." type="journal article" year="1834">
Erichson, 
<number box="[264,326,1044,1070]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1834.0">1834</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, which should be also included in the Curina as a rather isolated, monotypic genus. It cannot be the 
<typeStatus box="[455,506,1084,1110]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1849" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1849" box="[639,963,1084,1110]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cylindrophora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[639,812,1084,1109]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Cylindrophora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier" box="[820,963,1084,1110]" pageId="6" pageNumber="11" refString="Solier, A. J. J. (1849) Orden III. Coleopteros, 105 - 380, 414 - 511. In: Gay, C. (ed): Historica fisica y politica de Chile, Vol. 4, 81 - 511." type="journal article" year="1849">
Solier, 
<number box="[904,963,1084,1110]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="1849.0">1849</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
which has now quite different content, as explained above.
</paragraph>
